Introduction

Chae Eunjung, formerly known as Enjel, is a South Korean singer under Starmade Entertainment and New X. She is a member of the girl group CLEO.She made her solo debut on February 26, 2007 with the studio album My Name Is Enjel. She was a member of Cpop girl group Girls Kingdom in Hong Kong. She was a contestant on Sing Again 3.
